OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FNon-Ukrainian Swansea      
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Frefugee refused free train 
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Ftravel                     
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, A Kurdish refugee has said he was      
OL,6, wrongly barred from using a free travel
OL,7, pass for eligible migrants because he  
OL,8, is not from Ukraine.                   
OL,10,FRaman lives in Swansea and was trying  
OL,11,Fto get to Barry, Vale of Glamorgan, for
OL,12,Fwork experience at a law firm.         
OL,14,FHe claimed guards at Swansea train     
OL,15,Fstation accused him of "abusing" a     
OL,16,Fsystem meant for Ukrainian refugees.   
OL,18,FTransport for Wales (TfW) apologised   
OL,19,Fand said it took allegations of racism 
OL,20,F"very seriously."                      
